✖️UNDEAD✖️
Smooth snake scales slide through the black slime of the decaying corpse. Through the ribs and into the collapsed throat, the snake protrudes between the witches necrotic teeth like a demons tongue. “SNAP!” The teeth snap shut on the snakes neck. Rotting tissue of the dead queen slowly reconstitutes as the snake is absorbed into the poisoned slime. Eyelids twitch and open to a sliver of white and foggy eyes. The undead predator awakens from her sleep😈
.
.
.
.

✖️WITCHCRAFT✖️
A Crisp wind chilled her sweat as she crept outside the cabin. As wind whistled through the dead black trees, it covered the sound of twigs and leafs beneath her feet.
A window, she hunkered below it and slowly rose. With one cautious eye she peered through the foggy yellow pane of glass into the house. Past the candles, flickering giving dim illumination, she could see her friend. Was it too late? Her rigid naked body of poisoned white flesh and black veins lay still. The witch had not finished her meal, she was near…
.
.
.
.

✨I’M MOVING!!!✨
Hey everyone! I’m relocating to Erwin Tennessee on the North Carolinan border starting July 1st!!!
I’ll be continuing work as usual from a private studio there that I will be working to slowly transform into something awesome, super exciting!!!

I’m going to miss my awesome Knoxville peeps at @black.moon.tattoo though so I’m sure I’ll be back on occasion to do a guest spot here and there.

Erwin is a pretty small spot but rest assured there is a major “tri cities airport” 30 minutes away and is accessible by lyft, Uber and rental car. There are hotels and air bnbs here too🙌.

I’ll hopefully be planting roots in this location for a while and am excited to see everyone here and get some awesome projects started!! 

You guys are the best, I’ll see you in Erwin!!!
